    <entry>
      <title>C++ Primer (1) 变量和基本类型(from chapter1~2)</title>
      <link href="/2022/03/02/cpp-primer/"/>
      <url>/2022/03/02/cpp-primer/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="C-Primer-（1）变量和基本类型-from-chapter1-2"><a href="#C-Primer-（1）变量和基本类型-from-chapter1-2" class="headerlink" title="C++ Primer （1）变量和基本类型(from chapter1~2)"></a>C++ Primer （1）变量和基本类型(from chapter1~2)</h1><blockquote><h3 id="Chapter-1——开始"><a href="#Chapter-1——开始" class="headerlink" title="Chapter 1——开始"></a>Chapter 1——开始</h3></blockquote><ul><li><p>for循环：初始化之后会检查边界条件再确定是否会进入循环</p></li><li><p>Window系统输入文件结束符：Ctrl+Z 然后 Enter/Return</p></li></ul><blockquote><h3 id="Chapter-2——变量和基本类型"><a href="#Chapter-2——变量和基本类型" class="headerlink" title="Chapter 2——变量和基本类型"></a>Chapter 2——变量和基本类型</h3></blockquote><ul><li><p>把算数值赋值给bool的时候，只有0才算false，正负数都是true</p></li><li><p>区分变量的声明和定义（用于分离式编译）</p><pre class="line-numbers language-cpp"><code class="language-cpp"><span class="token keyword">extern</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> i<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//声明</span><span class="token keyword">extern</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> i<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">99</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//定义</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li><li><p>变量声明规范: 变量小写，类名首字母大写</p></li><li><p>引用：相当于给已有对象起了别名，必须被某一个对象初始化。（&amp; 有时候代表取地址符，而不是表示引用，要区分）</p><pre class="line-numbers language-cpp"><code class="language-cpp"><span class="token keyword">int</span> val<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">1024</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token operator">&amp;</span>reval<span class="token operator">=</span>val<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//初始化引用，初始化的&amp;只表示这个变量是引用变量，只是声明的一部分，没有其他含义。</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li><li><p>指针：存放某个变量的地址，本身相当于一个对象。（引用不是对象没有实际地址，故不能定义指向引用的指针。</p><pre class="line-numbers language-cpp"><code class="language-cpp"><span class="token keyword">int</span> val<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">1024</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token operator">*</span>reval<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token operator">&amp;</span>val<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//初始化指针，初始化的*只表示这个变量是指针变量，只是声明的一部分，没有解引用的含义。</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//右边的&amp;表示取地址</span>cout<span class="token operator">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="token operator">*</span>reval<span class="token operator">&lt;&lt;</span>endl<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//使用解引用符号*访问指针所指向的变量内容 </span><span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token operator">*</span>p1<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token keyword">nullptr</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//初始化空指针，尽量避免使用NULL</span><span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token operator">*</span>p2<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token operator">&amp;</span>val<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// void指针，可以指向任何类型的变量，但不能对地址上的内容进行操作</span><span class="token keyword">int</span><span class="token operator">*</span> k1<span class="token punctuation">,</span>k2<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//只有k1是指针，k2是int变量，建议*和变量名写在一起</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token operator">*</span>p<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token operator">*</span><span class="token operator">&amp;</span>r<span class="token operator">=</span>p<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//指向指针的引用，从右向左看容易理解变量的含义</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li><li><p>const和指针<br>顶层const：表示指针本身是个常量</p><pre class="line-numbers language-cpp"><code class="language-cpp"><span class="token keyword">int</span> i<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token operator">*</span><span class="token keyword">const</span> p1<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token operator">&amp;</span>i<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//顶层const</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>底层const：指针指向的对象是个常量</p><pre class="line-numbers language-cpp"><code class="language-cpp"><span class="token keyword">const</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> x<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">42</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">const</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token operator">*</span>p2<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token operator">&amp;</span>x<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//底层const</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li><li><p>decltype类型指示符</p><pre class="line-numbers language-cpp"><code class="language-cpp"><span class="token keyword">const</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> i<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">decltype</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>i<span class="token punctuation">)</span> x<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// decltype(i)==const int</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li><li><p>预处理指令——头文件保护符</p><pre class="line-numbers language-cpp"><code class="language-cpp"><span class="token macro property">#<span class="token directive keyword">define</span> </span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//把一个名字设成预处理变量</span><span class="token macro property">#<span class="token directive keyword">ifdef</span>(变量已定义时为真) / #<span class="token directive keyword">ifndef</span>（变量未定义时为真）</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//如果判断条件为真，就执行至#endif</span><span class="token macro property">#<span class="token directive keyword">endif</span></span><span class="token macro property">#<span class="token directive keyword">elif</span></span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/* 若#if, #ifdef, #ifndef或前面的#elif条件不满足，则执行#elif之后的语句，相当于C语法中的else-if*/</span><span class="token macro property">#<span class="token directive keyword">else</span> </span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/* 与#if, #ifdef, #ifndef对应, 若这些条件不满足，则执行#else之后的语句，相当于C语法中的else */</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> C++ </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> C++ </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Markdown入门学习笔记</title>
      <link href="/2022/03/02/article-title/"/>
      <url>/2022/03/02/article-title/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Markdown学习入门笔记"><a href="#Markdown学习入门笔记" class="headerlink" title="Markdown学习入门笔记"></a>Markdown学习入门笔记</h1><blockquote><h2 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a><strong>标题</strong></h2><pre><code>n号标题：在文字加前n个#号</code></pre><h2 id="段落"><a href="#段落" class="headerlink" title="段落"></a><strong>段落</strong></h2><pre><code>空格：使用两个以上空格加上回车</code></pre><h2 id="文字"><a href="#文字" class="headerlink" title="文字"></a><strong>文字</strong></h2><pre><code>*斜体文本***粗体文本*****粗斜体文本***</code></pre><h2 id="线段"><a href="#线段" class="headerlink" title="线段"></a><strong>线段</strong></h2><pre><code>分隔线：***删除线：~~文字两端~~下划线：&lt;u&gt;带下划线文本&lt;/u&gt;脚注：[^要注明的文本]</code></pre><h2 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a><strong>列表</strong></h2><pre><code>无序列表：* 文字有序列表：1. 文字列表嵌套：对子列表前面使用Tab建</code></pre><h2 id="区块"><a href="#区块" class="headerlink" title="区块"></a><strong>区块</strong></h2><pre><code>区块：&gt; 文字区块嵌套： 在之前一&gt;的基础上，&gt; &gt; 文字</code></pre><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a><strong>代码</strong></h2><pre><code>文字内代码：&#39;code&#39;代码区块：```         code         ```</code></pre><h2 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a><strong>链接</strong></h2><pre><code>[链接名称](链接地址)&lt;链接地址&gt; eg: &lt;https://www.google.com&gt;</code></pre><h2 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a><strong>图片</strong></h2><pre><code>![Alt text](图片链接 &quot;optional title&quot;)Alt text：图片的Alt标签，用来描述图片的关键词，可以不写。最初的本意是当图片因为某种原因不能被显示时而出现的替代文字，后来又被用于SEO，可以方便搜索引擎根据Alt text里面的关键词搜索到图片。图片链接：可以是图片的本地地址或者是网址。&quot;optional title&quot;：鼠标悬置于图片上会出现的标题文字，可以不写。eg:![RUNOOB 图标](http://static.runoob.com/images/runoob-logo.png)![RUNOOB 图标](http://static.runoob.com/images/runoob-logo.png &quot;RUNOOB&quot;)</code></pre><pre><code>指定图像高度宽度：&lt;img src=&quot;http://static.runoob.com/images/runoob-logo.png&quot; width=&quot;50%&quot;&gt;</code></pre><h2 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a><strong>表格</strong></h2><pre><code>|  表头   | 表头  ||  ----  | ----  || 单元格  | 单元格 || 单元格  | 单元格 |</code></pre><pre><code>| 左对齐 | 右对齐 | 居中对齐 || :-----| ----: | :----: || 单元格 | 单元格 | 单元格 || 单元格 | 单元格 | 单元格 |</code></pre><p><img src="//lee-abcde.github.io/2022/03/02/article-title/wlop-23se.jpg" alt></p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 前端 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Markdown </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
